description: Our Summer Smackdown quarter final matches begin with muscled hunks Jessie "Cut-Throat" Colter and Mitch "The Machine" Vaughn as they prepare to fight balls to the wall for a chance to move one step closer to the gold belt. The Machine uses his giant thighs to wrap up his opponent with vicious leg locks while Cut-Throat plays dirty and relentlessly tickles the hell out of The Machine. The points are tallied up after three grueling rounds and only one man can come out on top. Will Cut-Throat prove to be the better warrior and move onto the semi final rounds, or will The Machine shut his cocky opponent up with a dick down his throat?
title: Naked Kombat's Summer Smackdown Tournament - Quarter Final Match One
